<item>
            <title>[HBASE-12819] ExportSnapshot doesn&apos;t close FileSystem instances</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-12819</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;While troubleshooting an out of memory error exporting snapshot to s3a, I found that ExportSnapshot doesn&apos;t close FileSystem instances it uses.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;An implementation (s3a e.g.) may depend on close() call so that resources are released.&lt;br/&gt;
ExportSnapshot should close the FileSystem instances upon exit.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
