                            <comment id="14268392" author="mbertozzi" created="Wed, 7 Jan 2015 22:24:08 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;why the inputFs is not closed too?&lt;br/&gt;
also what about the inputFs and outputFs in the ExportMapper? implement the cleanup() method and close them there?&lt;br/&gt;
(not sure if the FileSystem instances are ref-counted. if not there may be more work for the mapper, to avoid that the mapper close() is thrashing the fs instances in the main when you are in the single jvm case, e.g. tests)&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
